Create account on github

Create one repository on github

Clone this repository to your local machine

Add file in repo

Commit this to your remote repository




#####For deploy app#############
git clone https://github.com/opstree/spring3hibernate.git
sudo apt update
sudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk
sudo apt install maven
mvn dependency:resolve
mvn compile
mvn test
mvn package
mvn install
sudo apt install tomcat9 tomcat9-admin
Add the below 2 lines(block of code) in /var/lib/tomcat9/conf/tomcat-users.xml

block of code->

<role rolename="manager-gui" />
<user username="admin" password="admin" roles="manager-gui" />

restart the service using -> sudo systemctl restart tomcat9

Goto-> localhost:8080

manager webapps
enter admin,admin(id,password)
upload war file


